Package eu.geclipse.ui

Interface Summary
IAuthTokenUIFactory An IAuthTokenUIFactory is responsible to provide UI elements for handling a certain kind of authentication tokens.
 

Class Summary
AbstractAuthTokenUIFactory Abstract implementation of the IAuthTokenUIFactory that provides methods for finding extensions of the authentication ui factory mechanism.
CheckSystemTimeSolution UISolution for checking the system time against a set of reference time servers.
DateTimeSolutionRegistry Solutions for problems connected with DateTimeText
Extensions This is a helper class that holds static fields and methods to easily access extension of the g-Eclipse ui extension points.
GotoWizardPageSolution  
LogExceptionSolution Solution implementation for logging an exception to the log and to bring the log view to front.
Messages Returns the localised messages for this package.
PreferenceSolution Concrete implementation of an UISolution that opens a preference page in order to point the user to the place where some erroneous settings may cause a problem.
ShowViewSolution  
UIAuthTokenProvider The UIAuthTokenProvider is the main point where Plugins should request their authentication tokens.
UIProblems Problem provider of the UI plugin.
UISolution Abstract implementation of the ISolution interface that is intended to trigger UI actions.
UISolutionRegistry Solution registry for all general solutions related to the UI.
